	keywords = {3G mobile communication; Global Positioning System; antennas; bicycles; carbon fibres; cellular radio; electromagnetic waves; production management; radiofrequency identification; sales management; 3G network; GPS; GSM; RFID; antenna; anti-theft; automatic control; bicycle industries; bicycle management systems; bicycle riding; carbon fiber materials; casual sports; container management; electromagnetic waves; global system for mobile communications; logistics management; production management; race; sale certification; stored value cards; transportation fee system; vehicle access control; Antennas; Character recognition; Fires; GSM; Logic gates; Tracking; GPS; GSM; RFID; UHF},
